  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Comparator Trial of a New Drug Against Genital Herpes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Double Dummy, Randomized Crossover Trial to Compare the Effect of &quot;AIC316 (Pritelivir)&quot; 100 mg Once Daily Versus Valacyclovir 500 mg Once Daily on Genital HSV Shedding in HSV-2 Seropositive Adults.</official_title>
