  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of &quot;AIC316 (pritelivir)&quot; 100 mg
      once daily compared to valacyclovir 500 mg once daily for the prevention of HSV-2 genital
      shedding.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
